Bomb (Su): At 1st level, the arcane bomber gains an ability nearly identical to the chemist's bomb ability. Unlike the chemist, at 1st level, the arcane bomber chooses one type of element from the following list: dark, earth, fire, ice, lightning, water, and wind. He can throw bombs of that type, but cannot modify them with discoveries. This ability stacks with the chemist bomb ability to determine the level of bomb damage, but an arcane bomber that becomes a chemist does not gain that class's bomb ability, nor does a chemist that becomes an arcane bomber gain this bomb ability.
