Apothecary
For various reasons - prejudice, lack of magical talent, or sheer contrariness - the apothecary eschews traditional magical methods of healing. Whenever a patient makes a miraculous recovery without its aid, the apothecary proves his worth, proves that magic is nothing but a convenient shortcut.
