summoned creatures, except that they are not sent back to their home plane until reduced to a number of negative hit points equal to or greater than their Constitution score. In addition, due to its tie to its evoker, an esper can touch and attack creatures warded by protection from evil and similar effects that prevent contact with summoned creatures.
